* social activities can be done in 2 ways: by the state or by the people; for all tasks : we decide between the 2 methods
* reasons against doing something by the state
	\ links-to internal wvaduwudofgzloxb
* the state size
	* has 2 dimensions
		* "horizontal" - the size of the territory of the state
		* "vertical" - the amount of acitivities that the state does
	* the state being big in any of the 2 dimensions helps it to be big in the other dimension